events.title: Adele
events.description: Having broken all records and topped the charts instantly, Adele’s latest album titled ‘25’ has become a gargantuan success. Featuring hits such as ‘Hello’, ‘I Miss You’ and ‘Love in the Dark’, Adele has proven to her fans worldwide that she is a world class singer who deserves their affection.

events.title: Andrea Bocelli
events.description: Andrea Bocelli has delighted crowds the world over for years with his distinctive tenor voice. Internationally recognized as one of the finest tenors of his generation, attending an Andrea Bocelli concert is a cherishable experience.
